The human+anthro thing would probably be a huge taboo in their respective societies. Human and anthro normies would probably be grossed out by interspecies relationships. The stigma means that they'd keep it private though, so keep that in mind if you know a human boy and anthro girl who hang out a lot, it's entirely possible that they are more than just friends, despite all they say in public.
